<?xml version="1.0" encoding="US-ASCII"?>
<document size="LETTER" margin-left="35" margin-right="35" margin-top="30" margin-bottom="30">

	<encryption allow-fillin="false" allow-modify-contents="false" allow-degraded-printing="true" allow-screen-readers="false" allow-copy="false"	allow-printing="false"/>
	<meta author="JIMS2, Harris County" creator="JIMS2, Harris County" title="Deferred Adjudication Closing Letter"/>

	<module>
		<font-def name="text" family="Helvetica" style="normal" size="10"/>
		<font-def name="text-large" family="Helvetica" style="normal" size="12"/>
		<font-def name="text-small" family="Helvetica" style="normal" size="8"/>
		<font-def name="text-italic" family="Helvetica" style="bold|italic" size="11"/>
		<font-def name="letterheader" family="Helvetica" style="bold" size="12"/>
		<custom-tag alias="letterheader" tag="paragraph">
			<attribute name="font" value="letterheader"/>
		</custom-tag>
	</module>

    <new-page size="LETTER" margin-left="35" margin-right="35" margin-top="30" margin-bottom="30">
    </new-page>
	
		<table columns="2" border-style="none" border-width="0" widths="15,85" padding="0" >
		<table-row halign="left">
	        <cell halign="left" valign="top" >
	            <paragraph>
	                <image source="MJCW/HarrisCountySeal.jpg" width="75" height="75" scale-to-fit="true"/>
	            </paragraph>
	        </cell>
	        <cell halign="left" valign="top">
	        	<table columns="2" padding="3" border-width="0" >
	        		<table-row>
				        <cell colspan = "2" halign="left" border-style="bottom" border-width="2" border-color="gray" padding-bottom="5">
							<letterheader>
								HARRIS COUNTY<br/>
								JUVENILE PROBATION DEPARTMENT
							</letterheader> 	
						</cell>
				    </table-row>	
    	        	<table-row>
    	        		<cell halign="left" border-style="none" font="text">
							Deferred Prosecution Unit (3 Months)<br/>
						  _if_( ${locationUnitName} notEmpty )
						  	<paragraph font="text">
						  		<b>${locationUnitName}</b>
						  	</paragraph>
						  _endif_
						 _if_( ${locationAddress} isDefined)
						   	<paragraph font="text">
								${locationAddress.streetAddress}<br/>								
								${locationAddress.cityStateZip}
						  	</paragraph>
						  _endif_
      				</cell>				
      				<cell halign="right">
						<paragraph halign="right" font="text-small">
							<b>${managerFirstName} ${managerLastName}</b> <br/>
							Caseload Manager<br/>
							Office ${managerPhone}
						</paragraph>	
				    </cell>		  	
		 		  </table-row>
            	</table>    
	        </cell>
		</table-row>        
	</table>
	
	<paragraph halign="center" spacing-after="60">
	<br/>
	${currentDate}
	</paragraph>
	
	<paragraph halign="left" spacing-after="20" font="text">
		${guardianName.fullNameFirst}<br/>
		${guardianAddress.streetAddress}<br/>
		${guardianAddress.cityStateZip}  
	</paragraph>
	
	<paragraph halign="left" spacing-after="20" font="text">
		RE: ${juvenile.fullNameFirst}<br/>
		Petition #: ${petitionNumber}
	</paragraph>
	
	<paragraph halign="left" spacing-after="20" font="text">
		Querido/Querida ${guardianName.fullNameFirst}:
	</paragraph>
	
	<paragraph halign="left" spacing-after="20" font="text">
		El juvenil mencionado arriba est&#225; programado a terminar la supervision por el Programa
		Diferido del Departamento de Libertad Condicional Juvenil del Condada de Harris. Adjunton esta
		un folleto titulado &quot;Estatutos Relativos a Acceso, Sellado y Destrucci&#243;n de Records Juveniles&quot;
		con informaci&#243;n del Articulo 58 del C&#243;digo de Familia de Texas.
	</paragraph>
	
	<paragraph halign="left" spacing-after="20" font="text">
		Las leyes en relaci&#243;n con el cierre de record y acceso automatizado son muy espec&#237;ficas. Por
		favor, revise las copias adjuntas cuidadosamente del la Secci&#243;n 58, Subcap&#237;tulos A y C del
		C&#243;digo de Familia de Texas. Los documentos detallan la disposici&#243;n de cada estatuto y su
		aplicabilidad.  Si tiene mas preguntas, deben dirigirse a su abogado.
	</paragraph>
	
	<table columns="2" widths="50,50" keep-together="true" font="text">
		<table-row padding-bottom="40">
			<cell></cell>
			<cell>Sinceramente,</cell>
		</table-row>
		<table-row>
			<cell></cell>
			<cell>${probationOfficer.completeFullNameFirst}</cell>
		</table-row>
		<table-row>
			<cell></cell>
			<cell>Oficial de Probacion Juvenil</cell>
		</table-row>
	</table>
	
	
	
    
</document>